data.description: Welcome to Greenbrier, neighbor! You belong here! This beautiful home is located in Hunter Heights at the very end of Valmont drive, on a spacious corner lot! Right around the corner is Matthews Park which has a walking trail, dog park, splash pad, playground, stocked pond & an ice skating rink! This stunning 3 bedroom/2 bath, 1,625 SqFt home has a two car garage & an even a shop out back with electricity! There is a covered back porch, perfect for entertaining, as well as an above ground pool with a deck! The backyard is huge & it’s filled with thick, luscious Bermuda sod surrounded by a wooden 6 ft. privacy fence. The roof was recently replaced in 2020 & the hot water heater was replaced 2 year’s ago. This home has fresh, new paint throughout, besides in the bedrooms. There are new quartz counter tops in the kitchen & bathrooms & updated lighting & fixtures. Wooden barn doors separate the dining & living room which has a charming fireplace. High speed, fiber optic internet is in this area! Award winning Greenbrier School District! A bike ride or short walk away from the Greenbrier Event Center where there is an indoor track & a basketball court! Only 10 minutes North of Conway!
